OL,3,CDisability: Lack of assistance by TfW
OL,4,C'makes me question my place in society'
OL,6,FA visually impaired woman says the
OL,7,Faccessibility of trains makes her
OL,8,Fquestion her "place in society as a
OL,9,Fdisabled person".
OL,11,FElin Williams, from Eglwysbach near ,
OL,12,Ftold the current affairs programme, Y
OL,13,FByd ar Bedwar, the additional services
OL,14,Favailable to the disabled community
OL,15,F"does not work 100%".
OL,17,F"The support doesn't always turn up,
OL,18,Fwhich really affects my confidence and
OL,19,Fhow comfortable I feel travelling.
