OL,3,CDisability: Lack of assistance by TfW
OL,4,C'makes me question my place in society'
OL,6,F"It is so important in terms of
OL,7,Findependence and enabling me to go
OL,8,Ffrom one place to another, and it is
OL,9,Fimportant that the support service
OL,10,Fworks so that I can keep that
OL,11,Findependence."
OL,13,FElin has a vision impairment called
OL,14,Fretinitis pigmentosa, which is a
OL,15,Fdegenerative condition. She can see
OL,16,Flight and colours, but without much
OL,17,Fdetail. Therefore, she relies on local
OL,18,Ftrain services to travel safely.
