OL,3,CDisability: Lack of assistance by TfW
OL,4,C'makes me question my place in society'
OL,6,FElin uses an app called 'Passenger
OL,7,FAssist' while booking a train journey.
OL,8,FThe app allows her to notify what sort
OL,9,Fof help or assistance she needs when
OL,10,Ftravelling.
OL,12,FWhen a request for assistance is
OL,13,Fapproved on a train, it is the
OL,14,Fcompany's staff role to provide the
OL,15,Fhelp.
OL,17,FThe aim of the app is to support
OL,18,Fdisabled passengers on trains across
OL,19,FGreat Britain, and is a scheme in
OL,20,Fpartnership with Network Rail.
