OL,4,C'makes me question my place in society'
OL,6,FWhen booking, Elin selects the
OL,7,Ffollowing assistance options: 'help
OL,8,Ffinding a seat', 'sighted guidance'
OL,9,Fand 'request priority seat'. She also
OL,10,Fadds at the bottom of the application:
OL,11,F'I need to be guided to the platform,
OL,12,Fonto the train to my seat, and off the
OL,13,Ftrain.'
OL,15,FElin recorded the help she received on
OL,16,Fa journey from Llandudno Junction to
OL,17,FRhyl.
