OL,6,FA member of staff met her at the
OL,7,Fstation and guided her to a specific
OL,8,Fseat, and said she would contact the
OL,9,Fteam in Rhyl to make sure they were
OL,10,Faware that Elin was on her way.
OL,12,FElin was placed in a specific seat to
OL,13,Fmake it easier for the staff to find
OL,14,Fher and escort her off the train.
OL,16,FHowever, although she waited after the
OL,17,Ftrain stopped, a member of staff
OL,18,Ffailed to meet her and she had to
OL,19,Fventure to the platform alone.
