OL,6,FWhile walking on the platform, a
OL,7,Fmember of staff did eventually make
OL,8,Ftheir way to meet Elin, but she had
OL,9,Falready got off the train. This is
OL,10,F"the most difficult part of the
OL,11,Fjourney", according to Elin.
OL,13,FThis situation was not new to Elin,
OL,14,Fwho depends on public transport for
OL,15,Fwork and socialising.
OL,17,F"It's a pretty common experience," she
OL,18,Fsaid.
