OL,6,FIn a freedom of information request by
OL,7,FY Byd ar Bedwar, the number of
OL,8,Fcomplaints last year about
OL,9,Faccessibility on trains had more than
OL,10,Fdoubled since 2021.
OL,12,FAccording to Elin, she has written to
OL,13,Fthe company several times over the
OL,14,Fyears with concerns about the service
OL,15,Fprovided to disabled people.
OL,17,F"I have never had an apology or an
OL,18,Fexplanation when I have complained
OL,19,Fabout the service," she said.
