OL,6,F"We have a right to an accessible and
OL,7,Fequal service to make sure we can
OL,8,Faccess society like everyone else
OL,9,Fwithout having to face barriers.
OL,11,F"But, of course, when those rights are
OL,12,Fnot implemented, those rights are
OL,13,Fruined, in a way."
